5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Newmarket"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Newmarket? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Newmarket, Kelvin Grove, Alderley and Wilston. Our 5-star instructors help Newmarket students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Newmarket is a densely populated core inner-northern suburb defined by the large commercial gravity of the Newmarket Reading precinct and the focused traffic volumes of Newmarket Road. The driving environment here is intense: students must quickly master rapid lane selection, complex signalised intersections, and heavy pedestrian interaction."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"For beginners, our instructors restrict lessons strictly to the quieter residential pockets bordering Alderley. However, the true value of learning in Newmarket lies in conquering the arterials. Driving from here directly through the inner-city bypasses to the Toowong TMR provides a masterclass in heavy urban traffic management."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Newmarket learners test at the Toowong TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from Newmarket, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"📍"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-gray-900 block mb-1","children":"N